label: uncl9509
comment: Code specifying a specific type of operand within a formula sequence.

values.label: Plus
values.comment: The formula sequence operand is an addition.

values.label: Minus

values.label: Multiply
values.comment: The formula sequence operand is a multiplication.

values.label: Divide
values.comment: The formula sequence operand is a division.

values.label: Exponent
values.comment: The formula sequence operand is an exponent.
